FX.name: Dual DLY
FX.description: This effect combines 2 delays and is based on the Eventide TimeFactor DigitalDelay.

Parameters.name: TimeA
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the delay time of Delay A.

Parameters.name: F.B A
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the Delay A feedback amount.

Parameters.name: TimeB
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the delay time of Delay B.

Parameters.name: F.B B
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the Delay B feedback amount.

Parameters.name: DlyMx
Parameters.explanation: Adjust the mix of the Delay A and B effect sounds.

Parameters.name: BAL
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the balance between original and effect sounds.

Parameters.name: Depth
Parameters.explanation: Sets the depth of the modulation. Also sets the output to mono (M0.M50) or stereo (S0.S50).

Parameters.name: Speed
Parameters.explanation: Sets the speed of the modulation.
